lyrics:
Доброта,
я люблю раздавать печеньки
и радовать людей!
Я очень счастлив!

[Verse 1]
In darkness we reign, fierce and bold
With fiery riffs, and tales untold
Our souls on fire, consumed by wrath
Black-metal's legacy, carving our path

[Chorus]
With every note, like thunder we roar
Ascending through chaos, forevermore
